text: Libeled Lady is a 1936 American comedy movie directed by Jack Conway and starring Jean Harlow, William Powell, Myrna Loy, Spencer Tracy, Walter Connolly, George Chandler. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1937. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1936 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Jack Conway
title: Libeled Lady
